The Art & Craft behind making of these larger-than-life Ravana for Dusshera.
Craftsmen from Bihar, Uttar Pradesh and Haryana have been working very hard for months to build the Effigies, they are particularly based out of West Delhi region. 
Most of the craftsmen are pursuing the craft for over 20 years. Some are specialised in making bamboo structures and others are an expert in decorating them with coloured papers and variety of paints. 
These figures of the demon king are made available from sizes like 20ft to 50ft and in variant vivid colours.
